Ow!

00:05:31.164 --> 00:05:32.915
You all right?

00:05:33.458 --> 00:05:34.334
Did you see them?

00:05:34.417 --> 00:05:37.211
Okay, there isn't much time
left on the clock, so we have to--

00:05:37.295 --> 00:05:38.421
Run!

