You guys…

00:06:07.075 --> 00:06:09.744
Do you really wanna
keep working for the Queen?

00:06:11.245 --> 00:06:12.789
Yeah, of course we do.

00:06:13.748 --> 00:06:14.916
We don't wanna die.

00:06:15.500 --> 00:06:18.127
If we keep playing for the Queen's side
and we win,

00:06:18.211 --> 00:06:19.754
then we can stay right here.

00:06:20.296 --> 00:06:23.257
If we're in this arena,
we don't need to play anything else.

00:06:23.883 --> 00:06:25.802
No getting hunted down or shot.

00:06:26.386 --> 00:06:29.764
