Just like us.

00:07:42.128 --> 00:07:43.671
Which means if we beat them,

00:07:44.380 --> 00:07:46.048
then there won't be anyone else.

00:07:46.924 --> 00:07:49.469
This will all end
if we win every face card game.

00:07:50.470 --> 00:07:52.763
That's just a guess, man,
and nothing more.

00:07:53.890 --> 00:07:54.932
Yeah, a guess.

00:07:55.892 --> 00:07:56.767
And hope.

00:07:58.519 --> 00:08:00.605
Maybe hope is what we need to survive.

00:08:01.230 --> 00:08:02.440
I won't give up.

