killing each other.

00:08:17.705 --> 00:08:18.748
That's not a life.

00:08:21.918 --> 00:08:23.836
Why don't you take a chance with us?

00:08:29.675 --> 00:08:32.553
This place
isn't that different from our world.

00:08:35.515 --> 00:08:37.892
You guys want to go back
to our world so badly?

00:08:40.019 --> 00:08:41.103
That place sucked.

00:08:43.022 --> 00:08:44.190
Maybe…

00:08:46.484 --> 00:08:48.194
Maybe this one'll be better.

00:08:59.455 --> 00:09:00.581
Yeah.

00:09:02.458 --> 00:09:04.168
I thought the same until recently.

00:09:06.212 --> 00:09:08.548
Going back might not be all that great.

00:09:13.010 --> 00:09:14.011
But you know…

00:09:16.514 --> 00:09:18.599
I want to go back, I really do.

00:09:23.479 --> 00:09:25.648
I wanna make it back to our world.

00:09:29.819 --> 00:09:32.029
For all the pain and heartache
I lived with,

00:09:34.490 --> 00:09:36.158
I was born and raised there.

00:09:38.494 --> 00:09:40.413
And it made me who I am today.

00:09:42.206 --> 00:09:43.541
I miss that world.

00:09:48.504 --> 00:09:50.631
At times, it was unbearably lonely.

00:09:55.136 --> 00:09:57.263
But I believe it taught me kindness.

00:09:58.723 --> 00:10:00.016
That life that I had…

00:10:01.559 --> 00:10:04.020
I'm kind here because it made me that way.

00:10:08.608 --> 00:10:11.027
This world makes kindness easy to forget.

00:10:19.243 --> 00:10:20.578
I want to return.

00:10:23.372 --> 00:10:25.333
I want to give that life another shot.

00:10:41.515 --> 00:10:42.475
I…

00:10:44.143 --> 00:10:45.353
I wanna go back.

00:10:49.440 --> 00:10:50.358
I do.

00:10:52.151 --> 00:10:54.904
I want to return and see

00:10:56.280 --> 00:10:57.365
my family.

00:11:15.758 --> 00:11:16.759
Do you think…

00:11:19.220 --> 00:11:20.429
Could I start over?

00:11:24.892 --> 00:11:27.645
Two turns remaining.

00:11:27.728 --> 00:11:31.482
Round 15 is the final one
for the Queen Team.

00:11:31.565 --> 00:11:34.235
This turn will last five minutes.

00:11:34.819 --> 00:11:36.529
Turn, start.

00:12:02.471 --> 00:12:04.849
They have 14 on their side?

