That's what you think?

00:16:43.919 --> 00:16:46.296
You have way more freedom here, you know.

00:16:47.673 --> 00:16:51.427
This place is much more my scene
than that rigid world.

00:16:52.553 --> 00:16:54.138
You were players, weren't you?

00:16:55.222 --> 00:16:57.850
You were brought here to play,
just like us.

00:16:57.933 --> 00:16:59.601
You had to play the games.

00:17:00.686 --> 00:17:01.854
Well, am I wrong?

00:17:05.357 --> 00:17:07.860
Oh, you'll find out soon enough.

00:17:07.943 --> 00:17:10.529
- Once the games are done.
- Not before then?

00:17:12.072 --> 00:17:14.074
What'll we learn when they're all over?

00:17:16.076 --> 00:17:18.537
First you clear all the face cards.

00:17:19.538 --> 00:17:21.165
Then you'll know everything.

00:17:22.458 --> 00:17:23.834
Will we learn where we are?

00:17:23.917 --> 00:17:26.003
Can we go back to our world?

00:17:29.173 --> 00:17:31.550
You'll have to wait and find out, baby.

00:17:33.093 --> 00:17:34.970
- Time is up.
- Hey!

00:17:35.471 --> 00:17:39.266
It is game over for everyone
on the Queen's Team.

00:17:41.060 --> 00:17:43.604
I wanna live free until my last breath.

00:17:46.356 --> 00:17:47.483
See you later.

00:18:37.407 --> 00:18:39.284
I want to finish these games.

00:18:40.744 --> 00:18:41.870
I want the answer.

00:18:44.998 --> 00:18:46.208
But more than that…

00:18:48.252 --> 00:18:50.170
I wanna go back to our world.

00:18:53.006 --> 00:18:54.383
Both of us together.

